OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying very
OL,6,Fwarm and humid overnight. Dry for most
OL,7,Fbut elevated thunderstorms possible
OL,8,Fovernight and in the early hours of
OL,9,Fthe morning. These could turn gusty
OL,10,Fwith hail and thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny early morning
OL,13,Fthunderstorms will move northward.
OL,14,FAnother very hot day to come as
OL,15,Fhumidity levels remain high. Very
OL,16,Flittle cloud to start but could see
OL,17,Fsome more later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
