OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fhot into the weekend, but temperatures
OL,7,Fslowly coming down; feeling fresher by
OL,8,FSunday. Some spots of rain and showers
OL,9,Fdeveloping at times, but lots of dry
OL,10,Fweather around too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
